{"tid":152963,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"港資老闆真係要幾閪有幾閪","createTime":"2017-03-12T08:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-12T15:52:55.000Z","uid":27225,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6fb9bd782ee48e379a460480a037b43f6c0f541","tid":152963,"uid":27225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T08:28:07.000Z","msg":"話說小弟最近轉工 就去左一間港資公司interview <br />\n由於我之前喺行內既一間大公司做過<br />\n一坐底個老闆已經係咁問我之前間公司係點運作有乜福利等等<br />\n我心諗你叫我黎面試定打探行情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話公司太多人黎見<br />\n好難先吱到lunch hour黎in我 心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問完一大輪先話開始進行面試 屌你老母<br />\n搞左一大輪 話自己仲有好多人要見就打發左我走<br />\n過左無幾耐打黎話比offer我，但就壓左我1k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話自己公司開支好大乜乜77 叫我考慮一下<br />\n(態度好好)<br />\n<br />\n到第二日 我已經一早打去accept offer<br />\n點知佢話個offer俾左另一個低價過我既人<br />\n最後仲cut埋我線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁無誠信學咩人做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw行頭好細 唔想開名<br />\n開名=自爆"},{"pid":"6e024ca15bb6843afd0811e7117aecd04a41b721","tid":152963,"uid":69531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:05:11.000Z","msg":"巴打邊行？"},{"pid":"548cd2602f77bf1bab6f4b896dd02533d243d8e1","tid":152963,"uid":55198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"似係套料多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1894e073e197a94c5afbdd2ae01e115c251e355f","tid":152963,"uid":59192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:10:30.000Z","msg":"價低者得"},{"pid":"3dd94966654c86b082dbe64d0fd26683a833379e","tid":152963,"uid":12788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T09:16:13.000Z","msg":"西公司入左去都喊三聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"245a10284021ef3c871ce69442aadf5c6cee6a35","ti